<br>
Then bandage if required before sitting and medding; I could safely handle any needlite I fought there with 60% health and 40% mana once I'd broken the spawn. The one exception was the needlite queen; let your pet tank that one with a DS (I was using water as I didn't have fire), nuke once when it has aggro and again when the queen runs.<br>
<br>
Did 25 to 29 here in a few hours at the weekend, and made about 220pp in the process; had to leave numerous needlite stingers to rot as well due to the LORE tag. I did find that they often resisted fire-based nukes, so was using the shock nuke instead... plus it's hard to hit anything in the cave with a bolt spell in any case.<br>
<br>
All in all, pretty safe, OK loot, and plenty of skill-ups; why go anywhere else? <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub102.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower.showUserPublicProfile?gid=ailurya@themagicianstower>Ailurya</A> at: 12/23/02 4:58:13 pm<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#dcdeed><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub102.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower.showUserPublicProfile?gid=eciypse>EcIypse</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.myoswego.net/~mojoteq/pics/17anidot5c.gif " BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Magician</span><br>  Posts: 21<br> <font color=#333333>(2/5/03 3:44:10 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerlevels2428.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=168.topic&index=12>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Needlites! Echo Caverns!</span><hr size=1> This place is not even worth it on my server. Always Permacamped, and the n00bs camping it do not ever know how to respond to a simple /ooc camp check. Whenever I tried, I would camp check 2 or 3 times, then I would run over. Every single time, some douche, often level 34, would be camped in there sitting on his butt, and when I would show up would say, &quot;Camped, I was on the phone&quot; Or some stupid BS. Also, the spawn, although safe, is terribly slow. There are definately better places IMHO. <p>      <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>&quot;Love is the answer; but while you're waiting for the answer, sex raises some pretty good questions.&quot; (Woody Allen) </em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub102.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower.showUserPublicProfile?gid=ailurya@themagicianstower>Ailurya</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Magician</span><br>  Posts: 40<br> <font color=#333333>(2/11/03 1:27:15 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezbo